{"comments":"Canvas — The Base Compositor Layer (z=0)\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThe Canvas is the **ultimate boundary container**. It is z=0, the back layer\nthat starts on load. Nothing ever goes \"behind\" it.\n\n## Responsibilities\n\n1. **Shadow Receiver**: Accepts shadows cast from all layers above\n2. **Boundary Definition**: Defines the rendering bounds for the compositor\n3. **Memory Boundary**: Critical for 3D scenes, game worlds, VR/AR where\n   content outside the canvas should be culled for memory efficiency\n4. **Clear Color**: The background when nothing is rendered\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nThe Canvas is pure data describing the compositor's root:\n- Same Canvas config = same rendering behavior (always)\n- Agents can reason about bounds without executing rendering\n- Memory management hints for culling off-canvas content\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Compositor.Canvas as Canvas\n\nmyCanvas :: Canvas.Canvas\nmyCanvas = Canvas.canvas\n  { width: Canvas.pixels 1920\n  , height: Canvas.pixels 1080\n  , clearColor: Canvas.transparent\n  , shadowConfig: Canvas.defaultShadowConfig\n  }\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["width",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"CanvasDimension"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["height",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"CanvasDimension"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["clearColor",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"ClearColor"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["shadowConfig",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"ShadowConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["cullOutOfBounds",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["origin",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Point"],"Point2D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[275,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Compositor/Canvas.purs","start":[256,16]},"title":"Canvas"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"Canvas"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[277,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Compositor/Canvas.purs","start":[277,1]},"title":"eqCanvas"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Compositor","Canvas"],"Canvas"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[282,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Compositor/Canvas.purs","start":[279,1]},"title":"showCanvas"}],"comments":"The Canvas — base compositor layer at z=0.\n\nThis is pure data describing the compositor's root container.\nThe runtime interprets this to set up the rendering context.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[275,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Compositor/Canvas.purs","start":[256,1]},"title":"Canvas"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a canvas with explicit configuration\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"co